  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game Introduction</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2259220/extras/6915ef8a6a3ead39e9177fa6f8203297.webp?t=1691779871\" width=600 height=10 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2259220/extras/9bd746130b3f8783a35bc69a4c00e989.avif?t=1691779871\" width=600 height=134 /></span><br>In 《伊甸园GARDEN OF EDEN》, you will lead an army to seek survival at sea.<br>The first problem faced by players as commanders is how to survive.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Unique settings</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2259220/extras/6915ef8a6a3ead39e9177fa6f8203297.webp?t=1691779871\" width=600 height=10 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2259220/extras/ebff93d4b7e862db4111b975f9d5cd19.avif?t=1691779871\" width=581 height=130 /></span><br>Unlike other settlement games, the survival location of 'Garden of Eden of EDEN' is chosen at sea.<br>The way in which most resources are obtained is brand new, and the difficulty will also increase significantly.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Rich entertainment</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2259220/extras/6915ef8a6a3ead39e9177fa6f8203297.webp?t=1691779871\" width=600 height=10 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2259220/extras/30b08f9d1b6ac04640a9f7ab14a91655.avif?t=1691779871\" width=600 height=130 /></span><br>To meet basic survival needs, it is also necessary to plan some entertainment facilities so that everyone has the opportunity to relax<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Weather System</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2259220/extras/6915ef8a6a3ead39e9177fa6f8203297.webp?t=1691779871\" width=600 height=10 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2259220/extras/4373220b280d82feaef1a40d6debff15.avif?t=1691779871\" width=600 height=130 /></span><br>Bad weather is the second difficulty, and the extreme weather that occurs in the game varies according to the season, resulting in unique negative impacts<br>If your strategy is clever enough, disasters will also be beneficial<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >A fierce battle</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2259220/extras/6915ef8a6a3ead39e9177fa6f8203297.webp?t=1691779871\" width=600 height=10 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2259220/extras/92ab3f7eb27aa00d31bb8ee1434da103.avif?t=1691779871\" width=600 height=130 /></span><br>When your wealth accumulates to a certain extent, there will be no shortage of bandits. Build powerful weapons and equipment to repel them",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game Introduction</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2259220/extras/6915ef8a6a3ead39e9177fa6f8203297.webp?t=1691779871\" width=600 height=10 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2259220/extras/9bd746130b3f8783a35bc69a4c00e989.avif?t=1691779871\" width=600 height=134 /></span><br>In 《伊甸园GARDEN OF EDEN》, you will lead an army to seek survival at sea.<br>The first problem faced by players as commanders is how to survive.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Unique settings</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2259220/extras/6915ef8a6a3ead39e9177fa6f8203297.webp?t=1691779871\" width=600 height=10 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2259220/extras/ebff93d4b7e862db4111b975f9d5cd19.avif?t=1691779871\" width=581 height=130 /></span><br>Unlike other settlement games, the survival location of 'Garden of Eden of EDEN' is chosen at sea.<br>The way in which most resources are obtained is brand new, and the difficulty will also increase significantly.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Rich entertainment</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2259220/extras/6915ef8a6a3ead39e9177fa6f8203297.webp?t=1691779871\" width=600 height=10 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2259220/extras/30b08f9d1b6ac04640a9f7ab14a91655.avif?t=1691779871\" width=600 height=130 /></span><br>To meet basic survival needs, it is also necessary to plan some entertainment facilities so that everyone has the opportunity to relax<h2 cla